Interface LabelAwareSentenceIterator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SentenceIterator
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LabelAwareFileSentenceIterator, LabelAwareListSentenceIterator, LabelAwareUimaSentenceIterator

    public interface LabelAwareSentenceIterator
extends SentenceIterator
    SentenceIterator that is aware of its label. This is useful for creating datasets all at once or on the fly.
